4 FORTH Word Reference
**********************

4.1 Stack Manipulation
======================

‘DUP ( n -- n n )’
     Duplicate top stack item

‘DROP ( n -- )’
     Remove top stack item

‘SWAP ( n1 n2 -- n2 n1 )’
     Exchange top two stack items

‘OVER ( n1 n2 -- n1 n2 n1 )’
     Copy second stack item to top

‘ROT ( n1 n2 n3 -- n2 n3 n1 )’
     Rotate top three stack items

4.2 Arithmetic
==============

‘+ ( n1 n2 -- n3 )’
     Add n1 and n2

‘- ( n1 n2 -- n3 )’
     Subtract n2 from n1

‘* ( n1 n2 -- n3 )’
     Multiply n1 and n2

‘/ ( n1 n2 -- n3 )’
     Divide n1 by n2

‘MOD ( n1 n2 -- n3 )’
     Remainder of n1 divided by n2

4.3 StarForth Extensions
========================

‘INIT ( -- )’
     System initialization from init.4th

‘ENTROPY@ ( addr -- n )’
     Fetch word execution count

‘ENTROPY! ( n addr -- )’
     Store word execution count

‘WORD-ENTROPY ( -- )’
     Display execution statistics for all words

‘TOP-WORDS ( n -- )’
     Display top N most frequently executed words

‘(- ( -- )’
     Comment to end of line


