5 Block Storage System
**********************

StarForth provides a comprehensive block storage system:

5.1 Block Words
===============

‘BLOCK ( n -- addr )’
     Return address of block n

‘LOAD ( n -- )’
     Load and interpret block n

‘THRU ( start end -- )’
     Load blocks from start through end

‘LIST ( n -- )’
     Display block n

‘UPDATE ( -- )’
     Mark current block as modified


